thread.title: Kathy

author: Kathy
title: Kathy
text: Plants were in great condition and ready to GROW. Shipped and packaged so well. I was so impressed, I immediately placed another order. In the past, I have ordered plants from other sources-at best I can say the plants were OK, but clearly stressed. I am delighted to have found a source for plants that are in excellent condition upon arrival and ready for my enjoyment for many years to come.
